..TEXT:
|Come l'augello~... |nasca~: These three opening
tercets, presenting the first term of a simile, are laden
with sentiment, as every reader will feel: |augello~, |amate
fronde~, |dolci nati~ {v.2}, |aspetti disiati~ {v.4}, |ardente
affetto~ {v.8}.
..TCHR:
